# ============================================================================
# Comments for Team Members
# ============================================================================

# This .gitignore is designed for the Animation Library project
# 
# Key exclusions:
# - animation_library/ folder (contains user's personal animations)
# - All .blend files (user animations should not be in version control)
# - All video previews and thumbnails (generated automatically)
# - Python cache files (__pycache__, *.pyc)
# - IDE configuration files
# - OS specific files
#
# If you need to commit example animations:
# 1. Create a separate examples/ folder outside animation_library/
# 2. Use git add -f to force add specific files
# 3. Or modify this .gitignore to allow specific example files